{"tid":1188514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"反送中條例今日有遊行!!!! !!!!!!!!!!!!","createTime":"2019-06-06T10:00:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T14:10:36.000Z","uid":22675,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9769c1d69836b7e722207b4bf14b06588c0e3aaa","tid":1188514,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T10:00:46.000Z","msg":"【引渡惡法●果燃台Live】法律界傍晚6時黑衣遊行 政總外靜默反送中<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190606/large/1559803435_cba6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190606%2Flarge%2F1559803435_cba6.jpg&h=5f24dce9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港府無視30名法律界選委及香港律師會等法律界代表一致反對，繼續硬推《逃犯條例》修訂。保安局局長李家超甚至批評，法律界因「不了解」修例內容才反對，法律界選委領軍入物、資深大律師陳景生要求與特首林鄭月娥和李家超會面討論，惟遭林鄭回信拒絕。法律界決定今午傍晚6時舉辦黑衣遊行，由終審法院遊行至政府總部。《蘋果》果燃台將現場直播遊行，觀眾屆時可按此觀看 。<br />\n<br />\n30位法律界選委和法律界立法會議員郭榮鏗今晚發起法律界靜默遊行，會是1997年後第5次。遊行在終審法院起步、終點是金鐘政府總部。遊行隊伍到達政府總部後，會靜默3分鐘，抗議政府修改《逃犯條例》。郭榮鏗早前接受《蘋果》訪問時解釋，因為今次矛頭是直指終日說「法庭會把關」、企圖「擺法官上枱」的特區政府：「以往嘅靜默遊行，係當件事發生咗，我哋出嚟表態反對，但今次係我哋反對香港政府一意孤行嘅修訂法例，法律界要行出嚟，係話畀香港人同國際社會聽，今次事態係好嚴重，我哋反對呢次法例嘅修訂。」"},{"pid":"a776755fb99089b1e5d6fa4d7be812d7b1abf7a4","tid":1188514,"uid":244332,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T10:01:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BSSpYPs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBSSpYPs.gif&h=88b0fdfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6/9，到香港人，銅鑼灣見"},{"pid":"4a8bdc7349f3565f560b208ddcaf64be97e1df64","tid":1188514,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T10:01:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190606/59683824\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190606%2F59683824&d=M59wMjr1KB2wSFKn0iQ%2BggESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=7c660649\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190606%2F59683824&h=b1bb9fd1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190606/59683824</a>"},{"pid":"a819d60d46a3e9008b53c8c9bb8c17bd4deb769d","tid":1188514,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T10:01:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e36fad489f1cebabdb01d253dec42c48bf26bfa4","tid":1188514,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T10:26:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"837c25c62229bf66e586a93acb35a7a72940d9c9","tid":1188514,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T10:26:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cc54f39ebe3130dd5575c191035a0b959f56fab","tid":1188514,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T10:27:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9fa0b38b2eda28562085be741cf52b72fdcc176b","tid":1188514,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T10:59:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"586a377b4084b736261dc53ce88c5f3787c156fe","tid":1188514,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T11:20:29.000Z","msg":"笑話<br />\n竟然話法律界因不了解先反對"},{"pid":"5ac047db9937de0164dc9ff933091e08afea1ede","tid":1188514,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T14:10:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}